name: Dark Theme for Google Docs [V2.0]
description: A dark theme for the Google Docs Suite, so you can get things done in the dark! This style currently supports: Google Docs, Sheets, Slides, Forms, Drawings, Sites, Classroom, Calendar and Drive. Check out my other Google dark themes: Google Translate Dark Theme Separate Google Classroom Dark Theme (separate version) Separate Google Calendar Dark Theme (separate version) Separate Google Drive Dark Theme (separate version)

user.name: Lekrkoekj
user.about: Hello there! I make dark themes for websites (mostly Google sites). I'm very inactive though

additional_info: New in this version: - Updated the color scheme to match Google's own dark mode color scheme more. Colors are taken from the Google Support and Keep pages. - Google Sites is now (mostly) dark again! - Added a new style thumbnail. - The 'You need permission/access to view this file' page is now dark. - Fixed the homepages and app chooser for like the 20th time. - The profile chooser is now dark again on Docs, Sheets, Slides, Forms, and Classroom. - The placeholder in the search bar of the homepage is now readable. - The Settings tab in Forms is dark again. - The Send Form dialog is dark again. - The scroll bar on the homepages is now dark. - The document overview on the side is now more readable. - A bunch of small fixes in Google Docs, Sheets, Slides, Classroom, Forms, and Calendar. I've started working on the style again! Currently making the CSS much easier to work with and fixing stuff.
